channel.title: Working Compiler for a 614?
channel.description:
Hey, I'm using Dementhium as a base, and their compiler for the source doesn't work for me. This is it:
[code]@echo off javac -d bin; -cp lib/*; src/org/dementhium/RS2Server.java pause[/code]
Can someone post their compiler for their 614 please? Thanks. :)
